PrecisRe-appointment of GIOVANNA ALLEGRA, of Gatineau, Quebec, and BANA BARAZI, of Outremont, Quebec, as full-time members of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Montreal Regional Office), to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years, effective April 20, 2001.
